⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of O'Brien
node 1984 · 1984 · ⟦O'Brien:1984:6b2a49⟧

WHO   — O'Brien — the inner Party · the trap
WHAT  — The betrayer and torturer: he lures Winston with the Brotherhood and the Book, then breaks him in the Ministry of Love.
WHERE — 1984 · 1984  Framework inputs: Nineteen Eighty-Four (George Orwell, 1949)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the deepest horror is that the resistance is the regime — that the hand offering escape is the hand on the rack.
HOW   — By feigned fellowship, the forbidden Book, and a torturer's intimate patience that seeks belief, not confession.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I gave you the Book and then I broke you on it — power is not a means, Winston; it is the end, a boot on a face forever.

